Revision history for Geo-Address-Mail

0.04    Thu Jan 13, 2010
    * Add standardize method as a shortcut for invoking Standardizers
    * POD reorg
    * Add new_for_country method as a shortcut (sort of like a factory for
      creating subclasses, if they are installed
    * Document MooseX::Clone method 'clone'

0.03    Mon Jan 3, 2010
  * Add MooseX::Storage depedency (thanks Andreas Koenig)

0.02    Tue Dec 28, 2010
  * Add MooseX::Storage (holophrastic)

0.01    Date/time
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

